"ngram\": \"a regular seasonMajor League Soccermatch\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American official also took charge of the 2023 FIFA Women's World Cup final in Australia.\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.998966920557923, \"rank\": 0.0007504191590254573, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999829958473664, \"rank\": 1.5092770930189098e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement Welch, 40, became thePremier League's first female referee when she took charge ofFulham's 2-0 defeat to Burnley on December 23.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burnley_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999875097646653, \"rank\": 1.24898138841133e-05, \"text\": \"Burnley\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burnley_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burnley_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Advertisement Welch\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"thePremier League's first female referee\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"charge ofFulham's 2-0 defeat\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has been refereeing since 2010 and became the first woman to officiate a match in the men'sChampionship- the English second tier - at the start of 2023.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first woman\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"a match\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"the men'sChampionship-\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"the English second tier\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Welch toldThe Athleticin 2021:\\\"My gender has never held me back in refereeing.\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athleticin 2021:\\\"My gender\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"refereeing\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is never been a point where I have come away from a game feeling that they have treated me a certain way because I am female.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"a game feeling\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They might treat me a certain way because I am a referee and they do not agree with a decision but I have not come under that scrutiny.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a referee\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"that scrutiny\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know other people who have.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ninety-eight per cent of people will not bat an eyelid when a woman turns up to referee their game, but there is another two per cent who will.\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ninety-eight per cent\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"an eyelid\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"their game\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"another two per cent\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In years to come, there will not be that exposure around it.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"that exposure\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That sounds negative, but it's really not.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will just be the norm.\\\"\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MLS's Drew Fischer has also been named as one of the 21 referees for the tournament.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\", \"score\": 0.9999998347343672, \"rank\": 1.6499698549573027e-07, \"text\": \"MLS\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Major_League_Soccer\"}, {\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drew_Fischer\", \"score\": 0.9999939576908413, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Drew Fischer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drew_Fischer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drew_Fischer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 21 referees\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Premier Leaguereferee David Coote, meanwhile, has been named as one of the video assistant referees (VAR) for the tournaments while MLS's Brooke Mayo and 